Subject: Re: [T2] Westfalia (Stockholm or Oslo) Interior question

They both have the bench seat, wardrobe, sink, stove as yours has.  I think
the difference is the Oslo has a full width back seat, and the Stockholm
has the 2/3 seat with another tall wardrobe (similar to the "common" westy
layout).

The Oslo is relatively rare. I'd guess the Stockholm is rarer.

